&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Account Executive&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt; Remote (US Central)&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Company:&lt;/strong&gt; Token Security&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stage:&lt;/strong&gt; Early-stage, high-growth cybersecurity startup&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p4&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Token Security&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;Token Security is redefining identity security by delivering complete visibility, deep context, and direct remediation for non-human identities and AI agents. We’re building a category-defining company and are looking for high-caliber sales professionals who want to make a meaningful impact, help shape the go-to-market motion, and grow with the business.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p5&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;As an &lt;strong&gt;Account Executive at Token Security&lt;/strong&gt;, you will own the full sales cycle within an assigned territory from prospecting through close. This role is ideal for a driven seller who combines strong enterprise sales execution with intellectual curiosity and the ability to collaborate deeply across Product, Marketing, and Leadership.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p5&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p4&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pipeline Generation &amp;amp; Territory Ownership&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;ul1&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li2&quot;&gt;Build, maintain, and continuously refine a &lt;strong&gt;prioritized list of target prospects, partners, and customers&lt;/strong&gt; within your assigned territory.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li2&quot;&gt;Leverage a multi-channel approach to drive consistent pipeline creation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li2&quot;&gt;Regularly analyze territory performance, pipeline health, and account prioritization to maximize efficiency and impact.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p4&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Value-Based Selling &amp;amp; Product Expertise&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;ul1&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li2&quot;&gt;Develop deep expertise in &lt;strong&gt;Token Security’s platform, use cases, and differentiated value proposition&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li2&quot;&gt;Clearly articulate Token’s business and security outcomes to technical and executive stakeholders, including CISOs, IAM leaders, Cloud Security teams, and DevOps.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li2&quot;&gt;Translate customer pain points into compelling, outcome-driven solution narratives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p4&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Opportunity Management &amp;amp; Execution&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;ul1&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li2&quot;&gt;Identify, qualify, validate, and advance sales opportunities through disciplined discovery and evaluation frameworks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li2&quot;&gt;Lead &lt;strong&gt;in-depth discovery sessions, demos, proof-of-value engagements, and customer evaluations&lt;/strong&gt; to increase win rates and deal velocity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li2&quot;&gt;Develop tailored sales strategies, formal proposals, and account plans for each opportunity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p4&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Competitive Positioning&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;ul1&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li2&quot;&gt;Identify and position Token Security effectively against competitive solutions in identity security, identity governance, and adjacent markets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li2&quot;&gt;Confidently handle objections and competitive bake-offs by highlighting Token’s differentiated capabilities and measurable

&lt;p&gt;Token Security is looking for a &lt;strong&gt;Senior Security Analyst&lt;/strong&gt; to join our research team. In this role, you will help uncover critical security risks in cloud, SaaS, and AI environments, with a strong focus on &lt;strong&gt;AI Agents &amp;amp; Non-Human Identity (NHI) Security&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will own hands-on security research across active customer POCs, conducting deep-dive security research on their environments, identifying vulnerabilities, surfacing real risks, and delivering clear remediation steps. Utilizing Token’s cutting-edge platform alongside hands-on manual research, you will translate complex security gaps into high-impact insights and executive reports, helping shape the way organizations secure machine and AI-driven identities at scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Frontier of Identity Security:&lt;/strong&gt; Token Security is a pioneering startup in the &lt;strong&gt;AI Agent &amp;amp; Non-Human Identity (NHI)&lt;/strong&gt; security space.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Research-Driven Value:&lt;/strong&gt; Our team focuses on IAM security across cloud, SaaS, and GenAI/AI Agent infrastructures, working hands-on with customer environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Customer Journey Partners:&lt;/strong&gt; Analysts play a critical role in POCs, uncovering misconfigurations and building actionable &lt;strong&gt;Security Reports&lt;/strong&gt; that move deals and guide customers toward a stronger security posture.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cross-Functional Impact:&lt;/strong&gt; You’ll bridge the gap between technical research and business value, collaborating with Product, Engineering, and Sales to drive product enhancements and help close strategic deals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead Security Research in POCs:&lt;/strong&gt; Conduct hands-on security analysis of customer environments using Token’s platform, manual techniques, and &lt;strong&gt;advanced AI tools&lt;/strong&gt; to optimize your research workflow.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Manual Environment Analysis:&lt;/strong&gt; Deep-dive into customer architectures using APIs, access keys, and tokens to expose weaknesses in IAM, machine identities, and AI agent permissions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Deliver Actionable Insights:&lt;/strong&gt; turn complex findings into high-level, impactful &lt;strong&gt;Security Reports&lt;/strong&gt; that outline significant risks and provide clear, step-by-step &lt;strong&gt;remediation guidance&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drive Product &amp;amp; Sales Excellence:&lt;/strong&gt; Collaborate with &lt;strong&gt;Product and Engineering&lt;/strong&gt; teams to share insights from the field and help improve the platform.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with &lt;strong&gt;Sales&lt;/strong&gt; teams to review environmental reports and confidently present security findings to customer stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stay Ahead of the Curve:&lt;/strong&gt; Continuously track emerging risks in cloud security trends, IAM vulnerabilities, and emerging threats related to AI agents and automation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Bring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4+ years of experience&lt;/strong&gt; in security analysis, cloud security, or offensive/defensive security research.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strong Cloud &amp;amp; IAM Expertise:&lt;/strong&gt; Practical knowledge of cloud infrastructure security, identity management, authentication protocols, and securing non-human identities/AI workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
